          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "A seafood buffet lunch with enough rice to put down a horse is on the table. It’s nauseatingly hot and I melt into the water. A Pet Co frisbee belongs to recycled plastic and not Fela. We hop back on the boat and find some turtles. Red haired woman gets a video call and aims the camera at Valentina’s butt while she’s bending over to look into the water. “Mzungus”. ",
